				</span><span class='av-structured-data'  itemprop="author" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/Person" ><span itemprop='name'>Jerry Newcombe</span></span><span class='av-structured-data'  itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2020-07-17T06:21:50-04:00" >2020-07-17 06:21:50</span><span class='av-structured-data'  itemprop="dateModified" itemtype="https://schema.org/dateModified" >2020-07-17 06:21:57</span><span class='av-structured-data'  itemprop="mainEntityOfPage" itemtype="https://schema.org/mainEntityOfPage" ><span itemprop='name'>The Antidote to Cancel Culture</span></span></span></article><article class='post-entry post-entry-type-standard post-entry-97670 post-loop-2 post-parity-even single-big  post-97670 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-commentary category-news category-policy category-politics category-religion-2 category-social-issues'  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/BlogPosting" itemprop="blogPost" ><div class='blog-meta'></div><div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix standard-content'><header class="entry-content-header"><h2 class='post-title entry-title '  itemprop="headline" >	<a href='https://drrichswier.com/2020/07/17/video-busted-black-lives-matter-is-a-jew-hating-organization/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: VIDEO: Busted! &#8216;Black Lives Matter&#8217; is a Jew-Hating Organization!'>VIDEO: Busted! &#8216;Black Lives Matter&#8217; is a Jew-Hating Organization!			<span class='post-format-icon minor-meta'></span>	</a></h2><span class='post-meta-infos'><time class='date-container minor-meta updated' >July 17, 2020</time><span class='text-sep text-sep-date'>/</span><span class='comment-container minor-meta'><a href="https://drrichswier.com/2020/07/17/video-busted-black-lives-matter-is-a-jew-hating-organization/#respond" class="comments-link" >0 Comments</a></span><span class='text-sep text-sep-comment'>/</span><span class="blog-categories minor-meta">in <a href="https://drrichswier.com/category/commentary/" rel="tag">Commentary</a>, <a href="https://drrichswier.com/category/news/" rel="tag">News</a>, <a href="https://drrichswier.com/category/policy/" rel="tag">Policy</a>, <a href="https://drrichswier.com/category/politics/" rel="tag">Politics</a>, <a href="https://drrichswier.com/category/religion-2/" rel="tag">Religion</a>, <a href="https://drrichswier.com/category/social-issues/" rel="tag">Social Issues</a>  </span><span class="text-sep text-sep-cat">/</span><span class="blog-author minor-meta">by <span class="entry-author-link" ><span class="vcard author"><span class="fn"><a href="https://drrichswier.com/author/ttrento/" title="Posts by The United West" rel="author">The United West</a></span></span></span></span></span></header><div class="entry-content"  itemprop="text" ><div class="at-above-post-arch-page addthis_tool" data-url="https://drrichswier.com/2020/07/17/video-busted-black-lives-matter-is-a-jew-hating-organization/"></div><p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-59148" src="https://drrichswier.com/wp-content/uploads/assata-blm.png" alt="" width="640" height="377" srcset="https://drrichswier.com/wp-content/uploads/assata-blm.png 640w, https://drrichswier.com/wp-content/uploads/assata-blm-300x177.png 300w, https://drrichswier.com/wp-content/uploads/assata-blm-450x265.png 450w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
<p>TOM TRENTO, Director of The United West introduces <a href="https://youtu.be/egJXGlsrDg8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Damon Rosen&#8217;s powerful expose of the Marxist organization &#8220;Black Live Matter.&#8221;</a> Not only is this terrorist group intent on destroying America but it also has its sights on Israel, working with Islamic terrorists, in a Red-Green axis, to destroy any and everything that has a Judeo-Christian foundation. How can any Jew or Israel-supporting Christian support this organization or movement?! Its leaders and spokespeople are openly hostile to the Jewish state and people.</p>
<p>It&#8217;s ironic that the people preaching against hate and intolerance, are among the most hateful, intolerant groups on Earth.</p>
<p>Damon Rosen is an investigative activist with The United West and currently lives and works in Israel.</p>
<p><strong>Please watch and share this video, especially with your family and friends who have been caught up in the media-induced hysteria.</strong></p>
<p><a href="https://youtu.be/egJXGlsrDg8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>WATCH:</strong></a></p>
