				</span><span class='av-structured-data'  itemprop="author" itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/Person" ><span itemprop='name'>The United West</span></span><span class='av-structured-data'  itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2020-07-17T05:58:53-04:00" >2020-07-17 05:58:53</span><span class='av-structured-data'  itemprop="dateModified" itemtype="https://schema.org/dateModified" >2020-07-17 05:58:53</span><span class='av-structured-data'  itemprop="mainEntityOfPage" itemtype="https://schema.org/mainEntityOfPage" ><span itemprop='name'>VIDEO: Busted! 'Black Lives Matter' is a Jew-Hating Organization!</span></span></span></article><article class='post-entry post-entry-type-standard post-entry-97666 post-loop-3 post-parity-odd single-big  post-97666 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-elections category-policy category-politics category-social-issues category-video category-waste-fraud-abuse'  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/BlogPosting" itemprop="blogPost" ><div class='blog-meta'></div><div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix standard-content'><header class="entry-content-header"><h2 class='post-title entry-title '  itemprop="headline" >	<a href='https://drrichswier.com/2020/07/17/podcast-the-press-is-failing-to-hold-liberal-politicians-accountable-mail-in-ballots-and-covid-virus/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: PODCAST: The press is FAILING to hold Liberal politicians accountable, mail-in ballots and COVID Virus'>PODCAST: The press is FAILING to hold Liberal politicians accountable, mail-in ballots and COVID Virus			<span class='post-format-icon minor-meta'></span>	</a></h2><span class='post-meta-infos'><time class='date-container minor-meta updated' >July 17, 2020</time><span class='text-sep text-sep-date'>/</span><span class='comment-container minor-meta'><a href="https://drrichswier.com/2020/07/17/podcast-the-press-is-failing-to-hold-liberal-politicians-accountable-mail-in-ballots-and-covid-virus/#respond" class="comments-link" >0 Comments</a></span><span class='text-sep text-sep-comment'>/</span><span class="blog-categories minor-meta">in <a href="https://drrichswier.com/category/elections/" rel="tag">Elections</a>, <a href="https://drrichswier.com/category/policy/" rel="tag">Policy</a>, <a href="https://drrichswier.com/category/politics/" rel="tag">Politics</a>, <a href="https://drrichswier.com/category/social-issues/" rel="tag">Social Issues</a>, <a href="https://drrichswier.com/category/video/" rel="tag">Video</a>, <a href="https://drrichswier.com/category/waste-fraud-abuse/" rel="tag">Waste, Fraud and Abuse</a>  </span><span class="text-sep text-sep-cat">/</span><span class="blog-author minor-meta">by <span class="entry-author-link" ><span class="vcard author"><span class="fn"><a href="https://drrichswier.com/author/ccrs/" title="Posts by Conservative Commandos Radio Show" rel="author">Conservative Commandos Radio Show</a></span></span></span></span></span></header><div class="entry-content"  itemprop="text" ><div class="at-above-post-arch-page addthis_tool" data-url="https://drrichswier.com/2020/07/17/podcast-the-press-is-failing-to-hold-liberal-politicians-accountable-mail-in-ballots-and-covid-virus/"></div><p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-94214" src="https://drrichswier.com/wp-content/uploads/Tlaib-Omar-Ocasio-Cortez-Pressley.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="370" srcset="https://drrichswier.com/wp-content/uploads/Tlaib-Omar-Ocasio-Cortez-Pressley.jpg 640w, https://drrichswier.com/wp-content/uploads/Tlaib-Omar-Ocasio-Cortez-Pressley-300x173.jpg 300w, https://drrichswier.com/wp-content/uploads/Tlaib-Omar-Ocasio-Cortez-Pressley-450x260.jpg 450w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
