<p><a href="https://click.mlsend.com/link/c/YT0xNDY3MjM4NDkwMTk3NDY0MjM3JmM9czJ3OCZlPTE5MjgmYj0zNzIyOTk5NjUmZD1yNWY4cDNk.56DaFwuAmTMIk9wmaZlYY0XAcSz11x946TWgxPVds7A" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://click.mlsend.com/link/c/YT0xNDY3MjM4NDkwMTk3NDY0MjM3JmM9czJ3OCZlPTE5MjgmYj0zNzIyOTk5NjUmZD1yNWY4cDNk.56DaFwuAmTMIk9wmaZlYY0XAcSz11x946TWgxPVds7A&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1595061668194000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGu7GTU7k41ekR06nLJU2ESUHsmQA">Russian Orthodox Church spokesman: conversion of Hagia Sophia ‘a slap in the face to the entire world Christianity’</a></p>
