<p><a href="https://click.mlsend.com/link/c/YT0xNDY3MjM4NDkwMTk3NDY0MjM3JmM9czJ3OCZlPTE5MjgmYj0zNzIyOTk5ODMmZD10OWQ3ejJy.61u_jKCH1m8ulnNZ0g2kgp1c8s7FNzDqSAcYeXXpAEc" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://click.mlsend.com/link/c/YT0xNDY3MjM4NDkwMTk3NDY0MjM3JmM9czJ3OCZlPTE5MjgmYj0zNzIyOTk5ODMmZD10OWQ3ejJy.61u_jKCH1m8ulnNZ0g2kgp1c8s7FNzDqSAcYeXXpAEc&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1595061668195000&amp;usg=AFQjCNFLm1QogGgJ5jBsl-wEofxvUE6EBA">Turkish Nobel laureate Orhan Pamuk on Hagia Sophia: ‘To convert it to a mosque is to say we are not secular anymore’</a></p>
<p><a href="https://click.mlsend.com/link/c/YT0xNDY3MjM4NDkwMTk3NDY0MjM3JmM9czJ3OCZlPTE5MjgmYj0zNzIyOTk5OTImZD1tMG80czVi.w7U8uOg_LcMx8tbiEqtsxZvstO6nhGfQPGypXmilrmg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://click.mlsend.com/link/c/YT0xNDY3MjM4NDkwMTk3NDY0MjM3JmM9czJ3OCZlPTE5MjgmYj0zNzIyOTk5OTImZD1tMG80czVi.w7U8uOg_LcMx8tbiEqtsxZvstO6nhGfQPGypXmilrmg&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1595061668196000&amp;usg=AFQjCNHk2j37meAHP2q6H4N6FHMw8PQ77A">India: Sufi Muslims threaten ‘law and order problems’ if film depicting Muhammad favorably isn’t banned</a></p>
