<p><a href="https://babylonbee.us14.list-manage.com/track/click?u=6753249476fcd9d02359150a6&amp;id=80069e4a16&amp;e=19cfa64f33" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://babylonbee.us14.list-manage.com/track/click?u%3D6753249476fcd9d02359150a6%26id%3D80069e4a16%26e%3D19cfa64f33&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1594981230550000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGs73-Ez13C-doGFaLTxOpXTm9oTg">Gavin Newsom Put On Timeout For Playing With Economy&#8217;s On/Off Switch Again</a></p>
